  "title": "🎁5day work !! High Commission !! Sales Beauty Consultant🎁",
  "description": "<p><strong>🎁5day work !! High Commission !! Premium Spa Sales Beauty Consultant🎁</strong><br /><strong></strong><br /><strong>Job Description</strong><br />Join Apex Wellness’s sales team to actively promote and sell premium skincare products,treatment and deliver expert advice, and build strong customer relationships to achieve sales targets and enhance the customer shopping experience.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Promote and sell skincare products and treatment  to achieve or exceed monthly sales targets</li><li>Stay updated on skincare product features and market trends to provide accurate and expert advice to customers</li><li>Assist customers by assessing their skincare needs and recommending suitable products to enhance their satisfaction</li><li>Demonstrate proper use of skincare products to customers to increase product understanding and encourage purchases</li><li>Build and maintain positive customer relationships by following up on their skincare needs and feedback</li><li>Collaborate with team members to deliver a seamless and enjoyable shopping experience for customers</li><li>Experience in the beauty or skincare industry with a focus on sales and customer service</li></ul><p><strong>What we offer :</strong></p><ul><li>5day per week</li><li>shift work time :10:00 a.m. to 7:00 p.m / 11:00 a.m. to 8:00 p.m.</li><li>Basic from $3500 - $4500</li><li>High Commission rate</li></ul><p><strong>What are you waiting for? Click Apply to join and be a part of Singapore's TOP Leading  Group!</strong></p><ul><li>PRIVILEGE BOUTIQUE ELITE - NAC</li><li>PRIVILEGE BOUTIQUE ELITE -PERENNIAL BUSINESS CITY</li><li>SPA - PRIVILEGE BOUTIQUE WELLNESS - WISMA</li></ul><p></p><p></p>",
